lead_paragraph: A two-time wrestling world champion said Tuesday he is giving up his place at the Olympics in Rio de Janeiro after a brawl marred a Russian qualifying tournament.

headline.print_headline: Wrestling Champion Gives Up Olympic Place After Brawl
